Package: internetdb
Type: Package
Title: Fast IP Lookups for Open Ports and Vulnerabilities
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2022-06-20
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bob", "Rudis", email = "bob@rud.is", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5670-2640"))
  )
Maintainer: Bob Rudis <bob@rud.is>
Description: Shodan <https://shodan.io/> scans the internet for hosts and services and maintains a few 
    APIs into that data. One API is the InternetDB <https://internetdb.shodan.io/>, which allows for
    free querying of open ports and vulnerabilities. Tools are provided to query this servce.
URL: https://github.com/hrbrmstr/internetdb
BugReports: https://github.com/hrbrmstr/internetdb/issues
